  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Great Phoenix has always been synonymous with spreading warmth on all who encounter them, you took this a bit literally. As a reaction whenever you see an ally using a jutsu with the Fire Release Keyword, you may expend a hit dice to enhance their own jutsu, choosing one effect from your Burning Bright Feature to apply to it.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-rank, expend 1 additional hit dice and choose one additional effect to apply to the ally's jutsu. Additionally, when choosing a different effect you can apply the same effect more than once.</p>",
